What ’ s your city like ?
It ’ s quite an interesting place to live . The best thing to do in my city is go shopping . There are several indoor and outdoor markets , department stores and shopping malls .
Is the traffic bad in the city centre ?
Not really . Cars are not permitted in several parts of city centre , especially in the main shopping areas . The public transport system is pretty good .
What about restaurants and entertainment ?
There are restaurants with food from all over the world . We have a small china-town near the city centre . There are many Indian , thai , and Italian restaurants all over the city centre . There are many s
